<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Ride Requested</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin:
      0; padding: 0; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding:
      20px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h1 { text-align: center; color: #333; } p { color:
      #666; } .details { padding: 10px; background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 5px; } strong { font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Ride Requested</h1>
      <p>Hello {{driverName}},</p>
      <p>A user has requested a ride and is awaiting your confirmation for the
        pickup time and location.</p>

      <div class="details">
        <h2>Ride Details:</h2>
        <p><strong>User Name:</strong> {{userName}}</p>

      </div>

      <p>Please review the details and confirm the pickup time and location as
        soon as possible.</p>

      <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>